    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, and it\u2019s never even seen a speck of rain! It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is the one. Come see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019ll fall in love at first sight! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
