    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional automotive specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle transcends the typical pre-owned category, offering showroom-grade aesthetic and mechanical integrity that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine cabin surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a pedigree of fastidious care. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
