    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in pristine, flawless shape. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed. It honestly still has that new car smell! If you want a top-tier vehicle without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
