    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is anchored by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing surgical precision through corners. This example is cosmetically flawless with zero bolster wear and original paint depth. Mechanically, it is turn-key with documented rod bearing replacement and a precise six-speed manual linkage, ensuring the visceral engagement only a high-compression, atmospheric power plant can provide.",
